orial","video":false,"overview":"When her son vanishes inside a US consulate, ex-special forces soldier Sara does everything in her power to find him — and uncovers a dark conspiracy.","genre_ids":[53,28],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.0667,"vote_count":621,"poster_path":"/micQGmD3K7Ni0wzyaSgBKGxrFWn.jpg","release_date":"2025-04-29","vote_average":6.61,"backdrop_path":"/14UFWFJsGeInCbhTiehRLTff4Yx.jpg","original_title":"Exterritorial","original_language":"de"},{"id":950387,"adult":false,"title":"A Minecraft Movie","video":false,"overview":"Four misfits find themselves struggling with ordinary problems when they are suddenly pulled through a mysterious portal into the Overworld: a bizarre, cubic wonderland that thrives on imagination. To get back home, they'll have to master this world while embarking on a magical quest with an unexpected, expert crafter, Steve.","genre_ids":[10751,14,35,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":24.2468,"vote_count":2787,"poster_path":"/yFHHfHcUgGAxziP1C3lLt0q2T4s.jpg","release_date":"2025-03-31","vote_average":6.282,"backdrop_path":"/2Nti3gYAX513wvhp8IiLL6ZDyOm.jpg","original_title":"A Minecraft Movie","original_language":"en"},{"id":1045938,"adult":false,"title":"G20","video":false,"overview":"After the G20 Summit is overtaken by terrorists, President Danielle Sutton must bring all her statecraft and military experience to defend her family and her fellow leaders.","genre_ids":[28,9648,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":3.3114,"vote_count":637,"poster_path":"/wv6oWAleCJZUk5htrGg413t3GCy.jpg","release_date":"2025-04-10","vote_average":6.428,"backdrop_path":"/k32XKMjmXMGeydykD32jfER3BVI.jpg","original_title":"G20","original_language":"en"},{"id":1195506,"adult":false,"title":"Novocaine","video":false,"overview":"When the girl of his dreams is kidnapped, everyman Nate turns his inability to feel pain into an unexpected strength in his fight to get her back.","genre_ids":[28,35,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":7.8449,"vote_cou